      <title>Creating a Bootable ISO from a Live Linux System</title>
      <link>https://wilfrantz.github.io/posts/2021-03-10-create-bootable-iso-from-live-system/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Mar 2021 11:33:00 +0800</pubDate>
